channel.title: How to start a Chapter?
channel.description:
We had so much help from Doug Merrill in Wenatchee this year that we adapted 5 ride-on cars this spring. Thank you so much @Room408
Can anyone tell us how to create our own Chapter in Redmond, WA and if it is necessary? Thanks so much.

item.title: How to start a Chapter?
item.dc:creator: Bill_Janes
item.description:
Good Morning and Welcome!

Details for starting a chapter can be found at: https://sites.udel.edu/gobabygo/contact/

If you need any help along the way, this board is a great place for support!
